text: ==Files
	<nextversion>This is an upcoming version. We are working on it! See [[ProgArm 0.2]] for current version.
	
	<undecided>Undecided</> / <todo>Todo</> / <done>Done</>
	
	==Improvements:
	* <done>Use newer and smaller barometer (BMP180? LPS25H?) -- **DONE!** (Using LPS25H[http://www.st.com/st-web-ui/static/active/en/resource/technical/document/datasheet/DM00066332.pdf] now)
	* <todo>Smaller bluetooth module (CC2541 with [[https://github.com/aanon4/BlueBasic BlueBasic]] or nRF51822 with [[https://github.com/pauloborges/blessed blessed]])
	* <undecided>Use SMD vibramotor. (But make sure that it does not get stuck)
	* <todo>Reduce size to fit into 5x5cm (4x7cm currently) to reduce costs. 4x5cm would be great!
	** <undecided>Use combined accelgyro and magnetometer (MPU9150?)
	** <todo> Use LPS4012-222L or LPS4018-222L instead of huge inductors.
	** <undecided> Smaller transistors?
	** <todo> 0402
	* <todo>Charge LED is disabled when the device is turned off. This leads to false assumption that charging is not working when device is turned off by hardware switch.
	* <todo>**Do not use rare components!**
	** <todo>Use bq24297[http://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/bq24297.pdf] with LM3668[http://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/lm3668.pdf] instead of LTC3566.
	** <done>bq27410[http://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/bq27410-g1.pdf] instead of LTC2942.
	* <undecided>Battery thermistor?
	* <todo>RTC supercap?
	* <undecided>No "mode switch"?
	* <undecided>Less ports?
	* <undecided>Add built-in voltmeter for self-tests.
	* <undecided>Add LED to indicate reflashing process.
	* <undecided>Pulse oximetry
	
